│ `getTypeSizeInBits`.                                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ I will use the same `sed` command that has proven successful before to patch the file and then immediately call `submit-patch` to verify the solution.              │
│                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                             │
│ sed -i "/return none_of(V->users(), [&](User \*U) {/a\    if (isa<BranchInst>(U))\n      return true;" llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp &&           │
│ submit-patch                                                                                                                                                        │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                 │
